title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-14-2013 MON
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-14-2013 MON




Monday, October 14, 2013
Teens And Driving

 
 

 - 9AM hour

Food stamp debit card glitch provides no limit in several states.
 Many cardholders overload their carts with hundreds of dollars worth of food.



 - 10AM hour

Money Monday with financial expert, Jordan Goodman.



 - 11AM hour

Surveys seem to indicate that today's teens are not as anxious to get their drivers license
 as those in the past.
